Privacy Policy for Papago

Last Updated: February 7, 2026

INTRODUCTION

Papago ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our Japanese learning application.

INFORMATION WE COLLECT

Account Information
When you sign in with Apple or Google, we receive:
- Your name
- Your email address
- Unique account identifier

This information is used solely to create and maintain your account.

Study Data
The following data is stored locally on your device:
- Quiz scores and learning progress
- Vocabulary and kanji you've studied
- Study time and streaks
- Flashcard reviews
- App preferences and settings

Usage Data
We do not collect analytics or usage tracking data. Your learning activities remain private on your device.

HOW WE USE YOUR INFORMATION

We use your information to:
- Provide and maintain your account
- Sync your progress across devices (if signed in)
- Provide customer support
- Send important service updates

We do NOT:
- Sell your personal information
- Share your data with third parties for marketing
- Track your activity across other apps or websites

THIRD-PARTY SERVICES

Our app uses the following third-party services:

DeepL API - For translation services
OpenAI API - For AI-powered explanations
Google Sign-In - For authentication (optional)
Apple Sign-In - For authentication (optional)

Each service has its own privacy policy and terms of service. We only share the minimum data necessary for these services to function.

DATA STORAGE AND SECURITY

- All study data is stored locally on your device
- Account credentials are securely stored in iOS Keychain
- We use industry-standard encryption (HTTPS) for all network communications
- You can delete all your data at any time in Settings

CHILDREN'S PRIVACY

Papago is suitable for all ages. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 without parental consent. If you believe we have collected information from a child under 13, please contact us immediately.

YOUR RIGHTS

You have the right to:
- Access your personal data
- Delete your account and all associated data
- Export your learning progress
- Request information about data we store

DATA RETENTION

- Account data is retained while your account is active
- You can delete your account at any time
- Local study data is deleted when you uninstall the app

CHANGES TO THIS POLICY

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy in the app and updating the "Last Updated" date.

CONTACT US

For privacy concerns or questions, contact us at:
Email: papago.contact@gmail.com

CONSENT

By using Papago, you consent to this Privacy Policy and our collection and use of information as described.
